  <h3>Example 1 — Performance Optimization</h3>
  <p>Claude analyzed the <strong>Chalk JavaScript library</strong> (~430M weekly downloads) and achieved a <strong>3.9× throughput improvement</strong>:</p>
  <div class="steps">
