    <div class="step"><div class="step-rail"><div class="step-dot"></div><div class="step-line"></div></div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Profile</div><div class="step-text">Uses profiling tools to find the slowest code paths</div></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-rail"><div class="step-dot"></div><div class="step-line"></div></div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Plan</div><div class="step-text">Creates a prioritized to-do list of bottlenecks to fix</div></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-rail"><div class="step-dot"></div></div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-title">Fix & Verify</div><div class="step-text">Implements changes and re-runs benchmarks to confirm improvement</div></div></div>
